Package com.jemonjam.versioneer.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CachedVersionLocator
    Caches the version from the underlying VersionLocator This will lazily check the delegate on the first call to CachedVersionLocator.getVersion().
    ClasspathVersionLocator
    Returns a version found from a file on the Classpath.
    FallbackVersionLocator
    Always returns a version as a String.
    FileVersionLocator
    Returns a version from the given file, using a UTF-8 charset.
    GitVersionLocator
    Returns a version from a git repo using the command git describe.
    PathVersionLocator
    Returns a version parsed from the specified path with the specified pattern.
    VersionLocatorChain
    Creates a chain of VersionLocator and returns the first non-empty version.
